(311, '_transient_dash_88ae138922fe95674369b1cb3d215a2b', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/11/wordpress-4-4-beta-3/''>WordPress 4.4 Beta 3</a> <span class="rss-date">November 4, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.4 Beta 3 is now available for download and testing.This is software still in development, so wedont recommend that you run it on a production site. To get the beta, try theWordPress Beta Testerplugin (youll want bleeding edge nightlies). Or you candownload the beta here(zip). For more of whats new in version 4.4,check out [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://ma.tt/2015/11/most-miles-of-road-texas/''>Matt: Most Miles of Road: Texas</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/justin-tadlock-explains-taxonomy-term-meta''>WPTavern: Justin Tadlock Explains Taxonomy Term Meta</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/easily-add-citations-to-quotes-with-the-better-blockquotes-plugin''>WPTavern: Easily Add Citations to Quotes With the Better Blockquotes Plugin</a></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li class=''dashboard-news-plugin''><span>Popular Plugin:</span> <a href=''https://wordpress.org/plugins/updraftplus/'' class=''dashboard-news-plugin-link''>UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration</a>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=''plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=updraftplus&amp;_wpnonce=99bfe0c338&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800'' class=''thickbox'' title=''UpdraftPlus Backup and Restoration''>Install</a>)</span></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
