k for a petition from one whom he believes to be a Mason.</p>\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Who are the Freemasons?', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-11-05 05:20:02', '2015-11-05 05:20:02', '', 11, 'http://127.0.0.1/boyer/index.php/2015/11/05/11-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
